<p>Dave and John are back in the saddle for another Monday evening filled with Mac geekery of all sorts, including answering your questions, solving your problems, and sharing your tips! This week&#8217;s episode includes a healthy focus on Mac OS X&#8217;s Dock, including a few tricky ways to customize it &#8212; want to add spacers to your Dock or customize which apps hide it? Listen in for that and much, much more!</p>
